:*在[[莫斯科號飛彈巡洋艦|莫斯科号导弹巡洋舰]]沉没后，马卡洛夫海军上将号接替莫斯科号成为了新的黑海舰队旗舰<ref>{{Cite web|title=Admiral Makarov to assume the new flagship of Russian Black Sea fleet|url=https://www.navalnews.com/naval-news/2022/05/admiral-makarov-to-assume-the-new-flagship-of-russian-black-sea-fleet/|access-date=2022-05-23|date=2022-05-19|work=Naval News|language=en-US}}</ref>
